docs.lead_paragraph: Not long after joining Aetna, the health insurance giant, Mark Bertolini almost died. A skiing accident in 2004 left his body broken and his prospects dimmed. He was in his late 40s and considered early retirement.

docs.abstract: CVS Health, the giant drugstore and pharmacy manager, will acquire one of the country’s biggest insurers, another sign of industry consolidation.
docs.snippet: CVS Health, the giant drugstore and pharmacy manager, will acquire one of the country’s biggest insurers, another sign of industry consolidation.
docs.lead_paragraph: The Justice Department’s approval of the $69 billion merger between CVS Health and Aetna on Wednesday caps a wave of consolidation among giant health care players that could leave American consumers with less control over their medical care and prescription drugs.

headline.main: CVS Health and Aetna $69 Billion Merger Is Approved With Conditions
headline.print_headline: Consolidation Of CVS Health With Aetna Wins Approval

docs.abstract: A federal judge overseeing the merger settlement wants the combined companies to keep some operations separate while he examines the $69 billion deal.
docs.snippet: A federal judge overseeing the merger settlement wants the combined companies to keep some operations separate while he examines the $69 billion deal.
docs.lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — A federal judge on Tuesday doubled down on his hesitation to approve the merger settlement between CVS Health and Aetna, asking the combined companies to take steps to keep some operations distinct while he completes his review.

headline.main: Judge Seeks Monitoring of CVS and Aetna During Antitrust Review
headline.print_headline: Judge Seeks More Scrutiny Of CVS and Aetna in Merger
